  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: General </p><p>You've learned that you are at your best when you're on the move.</p><p> You gain the following benefits: </p><p>• Your speed increases by 10 feet.</p><p>• When you would make a Dexterity saving throw on your turn, you gain a +2 bonus to the save.</p><p>• Once per turn, when you move at least 10 feet, you gain a 1d4 bonus to your next attack roll before the end of the current turn.</p><p>• When you make a melee attack against a creature, you don't provoke opportunity attacks from that creature for the rest of the turn, whether you hit or not.</p><p></p>",
